snippet.title: Giant Bomb
snippet.description: Giant Bomb is here to give you what you need when it comes to the world of video games, new and old. Fire up a Quick Look, sit back, and enjoy, friends. We post videos nearly every day, so subscribe and stick around for awhile. Cool?
